fields.name: BUKRAM COLLAR
fields.description:
The Bukram collar has a striking blue Ikat pattern which makes it beautifully eye-catching when worn by your furry companion!

All our dog collars and leads are made from cotton fabrics, bicycle inner-tubes and matching steel hardware.  To add to the strength of the product we include a durable polyester webbing sandwiched between the layers of fabric and finish each product with a (vegan) wax coating for water resistance.

Both the fabric and inner tubes are recycled materials sourced from local markets close to our workshop in India.

Washing Instructions:

Please hand wash with warm water and mild detergent.

fields.name: TOLLA BANDANA
fields.description:
The Tolla bandana is a beautiful multi-coloured Ikat bandana with a striking pink pompom.

Ikat is a dyeing technique used to pattern textiles. The weavers use resist dyeing on the yarns prior to weaving the fabric. All our Ikat dog bandanas are made from fabric sourced from trusted suppliers in Kolkata. 

Sizes:

S/M - Fits Dog Collars from 24-40cm (fits our S/M collars perfectly!)
M/L -Fits Dog Collars from 40cm-53cm (fits our M/L collars perfectly!)

fields.name: BLUE WASTE BAG DISPENSER
fields.description:
Our dog waste bag dispensers are a functional addition to your dog walks, best attached to our dog leads with a split ring included and can be clipped onto your trousers or travel bag.

Other features include:

~ Organic hemp lining
~ Includes one roll of earth rated biodegradable poo bags
~ Recycled bicycle inner tube details
~ Snap fastening at the back to easily change the roll of bags
~ Vegan/Plastic free eco friendly 
~ Match our range of dog collars & leads to complete a set

Dimensions:

From the clip to the bottom length - 17.5cm X 6.5cm
Fabric length - 10.5cm X 6.5cm

Washing:

These prefer to be hand-washed, however if this is not possible please machine wash no higher than 30°c inside a pillow case to cushion the metal clip.
